Extension: Nepal Address

Official URL: https://fhir.hmis.gov.np/StructureDefinition/NepalAddress Version: 0.0.1-ballot
Active as of 2025-09-04 Computable Name: NepalAddressEx

Copyright/Legal: Used by permission of HL7 International, all rights reserved Creative Commons License

Extension to represent coded and textual forms of Nepal's administrative divisions (Province, District, Municipality, Ward).

Context of Use

    This extension may be used on the following element(s)

    • Element ID: Address

Usage info

Usages:

  • Use this Extension: NP Core Patient Profile
  • Examples for this Extension: Patient/patient-child and Patient/patient-pregnant

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
